trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of controls contained on a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" />.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de controles contenida en un control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control returns an instance of type <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection> which you can cast to an instance of type <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> propiedad de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control devuelve una instancia del tipo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ControlCollection> que puede convertirse en una instancia del tipo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection> includes controls such as the editing control and the scrollbars on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection> incluye controles como el control de edición y las barras de desplazamiento en el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" /> that owns the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" /> que posee <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes all controls from the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" />.
trans-unit.target: Quita todos los controles del control <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection.Clear%2A> method removes all controls from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>, except the scroll bars and the editing control.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection.Clear%2A> método quita todos los controles de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>, excepto las barras de desplazamiento y el control de edición.

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> array that is the destination of the elements copied from the current collection.
trans-unit.target: Matriz de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> unidimensional que constituye el destino de los elementos copiados desde la colección actual.

trans-unit.source: The array must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: La matriz debe tener una indización de base cero.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>array</c> at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero de <c>array</c> donde comienza la copia.

trans-unit.source: Copies the contents of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" /> into a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia el contenido de la colección <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" /> en una matriz <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" />, empezando en el índice especificado de la matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> es <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> es menor que cero.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> es multidimensional.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: O bien

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source collection is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: El número de elementos en la colección de origen es mayor que el espacio disponible desde <paramref name="index" /> hasta el final de <paramref name="array" />.

trans-unit.source: The type of the source element cannot be cast automatically to the type of <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: El tipo del elemento de origen no puede convertirse automáticamente al tipo de <paramref name="array" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert <c>value</c>.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero donde se va a insertar <c>value</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> to insert into the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> que se va a insertar en <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Inserts the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Inserta el objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> especificado en el índice especificado de la colección <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero or greater than or equal to the current number of controls in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> es menor que cero o mayor o igual que el número actual de controles contenidos en la colección <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> to remove from the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Control" /> que se va a quitar de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified control from the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Quita el control especificado de la colección <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataGridViewControlCollection" />.
